# Security & Moderation

- **No Over-claiming Legal Rights**: Never imply that Orignym registration grants legal ownership or trademark clearance.
- **Audit Logging**: Persist model/provider/prompt metadata for all AI-driven operations. Log all moderation and publication events to `AuditEvent`.
- **RBAC**: Do not mix user data. Only admins can freeze/unpublish claims.
- Never commit secrets or expose API keys. 
- AI outputs must be bounded by system prompts and filtered for misuse.